overview: Cory has experience with International Armoring in Spain and as an entrepreneur domestically in negotiating cost-effective vendor relationships, setting up win-win partnerships and building business processes that work. The strength and effectiveness of the EnticeLabs service is directly tied to the success of Cory’s team in building a comprehensive, diverse, and continually growing publisher network. Cory holds a Bachelors degree in Economics from Brigham Young University.
